cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.SY. 

The paper deals with reinforcement learning algorithms and their application in safety-critical systems, which suggests cs.AI and cs.RO as likely categories. The focus on learning to switch control between machines and humans suggests cs.HC as another likely category. The use of upper confidence bounds and regret analysis suggests cs.LG as a possible category. Finally, the application of the proposed algorithms in autonomous driving systems suggests cs.SY as a possible category.
